# 📚 Students Attendance Monitor System

A smart attendance monitoring system designed to track and manage student attendance efficiently using barcode scanning technology and real-time notifications.

## 🚀 Features

- 📷 Barcode/QR Code based attendance marking
- 📊 Real-time attendance tracking
- 🔔 Instant notification alerts to students
- 🚌 Bus tracking and arrival notification
- 👩‍🏫 Admin dashboard for monitoring attendance
- 📁 Attendance report generation

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- Python
- Flask / Django (Backend)
- MySQL / SQLite (Database)
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript (Frontend)
- Git & GitHub

